name: BloodyScreen
body:
## 5.0.0 Release
- Updated for 5.3
- Recoded textures to RLE targa.
- Removed crap from the code.
- Renamed some files.
- Fixed typos.
- Fixed frames.
- Fixed missing localization phrases.
- Minimun and maxium damage default value is now 25000 and 50000.
- Damage "-+" buttons now have +-1000 value.
- Total code cleanup.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
